{"surah":{"number":77,"name":"المرسلات","englishName":"Al-Mursalat","englishTranslation":"The Emissaries","ayahCount":50},"sources":["Quran.com API v4 (word-by-word Uthmani + English glosses + word audio)","AlQuran.cloud / Tanzil quran-uthmani (independent text verification)","AlQuran.cloud / Saheeh International (flowing English translation)","Quranic Arabic Corpus morphology (word roots)"],"generatedAt":"2026-07-03T04:01:37.031Z","ayahs":[{"number":1,"translation":"By those [winds] sent forth in gusts","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلْمُرْسَلَـٰتِ","english":"By the ones sent forth","translit":"wal-mur'salāti","root":"رسل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عُرْفًۭا","english":"one after another","translit":"ʿur'fan","root":"عرف"}]},{"number":2,"translation":"And the winds that blow violently","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْعَـٰصِفَـٰتِ","english":"And the winds that blow","translit":"fal-ʿāṣifāti","root":"عصف"},{"position":2,"arabic":"عَصْفًۭا","english":"violently","translit":"ʿaṣfan","root":"عصف"}]},{"number":3,"translation":"And [by] the winds that spread [clouds]","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّـٰشِرَٰتِ","english":"And the ones that scatter","translit":"wal-nāshirāti","root":"نشر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَشْرًۭا","english":"far and wide","translit":"nashran","root":"نشر"}]},{"number":4,"translation":"And those [angels] who bring criterion","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْفَـٰرِقَـٰتِ","english":"And those who separate","translit":"fal-fāriqāti","root":"فرق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَرْقًۭا","english":"(by the) Criterion","translit":"farqan","root":"فرق"}]},{"number":5,"translation":"And those [angels] who deliver a message","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَٱلْمُلْقِيَـٰتِ","english":"And those who bring down","translit":"fal-mul'qiyāti","root":"لقي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ذِكْرًا","english":"(the) Reminder","translit":"dhik'ran","root":"ذكر"}]},{"number":6,"translation":"As justification or warning,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"عُذْرًا","english":"(As) justification","translit":"ʿudh'ran","root":"عذر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَوْ","english":"or","translit":"aw","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نُذْرًا","english":"warning","translit":"nudh'ran","root":"نذر"}]},{"number":7,"translation":"Indeed, what you are promised is to occur.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا","english":"Indeed, what","translit":"innamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تُوعَدُونَ","english":"you are promised","translit":"tūʿadūna","root":"وعد"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَوَٰقِعٌۭ","english":"will surely occur","translit":"lawāqiʿun","root":"وقع"}]},{"number":8,"translation":"So when the stars are obliterated","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِذَا","english":"So when","translit":"fa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلنُّجُومُ","english":"the stars","translit":"l-nujūmu","root":"نجم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"طُمِسَتْ","english":"are obliterated","translit":"ṭumisat","root":"طمس"}]},{"number":9,"translation":"And when the heaven is opened","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءُ","english":"the heaven","translit":"l-samāu","root":"سمو"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فُرِجَتْ","english":"is cleft asunder","translit":"furijat","root":"فرج"}]},{"number":10,"translation":"And when the mountains are blown away","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْجِبَالُ","english":"the mountains","translit":"l-jibālu","root":"جبل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"نُسِفَتْ","english":"are blown away","translit":"nusifat","root":"نسف"}]},{"number":11,"translation":"And when the messengers' time has come...","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلرُّسُلُ","english":"the Messengers","translit":"l-rusulu","root":"رسل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أُقِّتَتْ","english":"are gathered to their appointed time","translit":"uqqitat","root":"وقت"}]},{"number":12,"translation":"For what Day was it postponed?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِأَىِّ","english":"For what","translit":"li-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمٍ","english":"Day","translit":"yawmin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"أُجِّلَتْ","english":"are (these) postponed","translit":"ujjilat","root":"أجل"}]},{"number":13,"translation":"For the Day of Judgement.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لِيَوْمِ","english":"For (the) Day","translit":"liyawmi","root":"يوم"},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْفَصْلِ","english":"(of) Judgment","translit":"l-faṣli","root":"فصل"}]},{"number":14,"translation":"And what can make you know what is the Day of Judgement?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَآ","english":"And what","translit":"wamā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"أَدْرَىٰكَ","english":"will make you know","translit":"adrāka","root":"دري"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْفَصْلِ","english":"(of) the Judgment","translit":"l-faṣli","root":"فصل"}]},{"number":15,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":16,"translation":"Did We not destroy the former peoples?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","english":"Did not","translit":"alam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نُهْلِكِ","english":"We destroy","translit":"nuh'liki","root":"هلك"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","english":"the former (people)","translit":"l-awalīna","root":"أول"}]},{"number":17,"translation":"Then We will follow them with the later ones.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","english":"Then","translit":"thumma","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نُتْبِعُهُمُ","english":"We follow them up","translit":"nut'biʿuhumu","root":"تبع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْـَٔاخِرِينَ","english":"(with) the later ones","translit":"l-ākhirīna","root":"أخر"}]},{"number":18,"translation":"Thus do We deal with the criminals.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","english":"Thus","translit":"kadhālika","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَفْعَلُ","english":"We deal","translit":"nafʿalu","root":"فعل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","english":"with the criminals","translit":"bil-muj'rimīna","root":"جرم"}]},{"number":19,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":20,"translation":"Did We not create you from a liquid disdained?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","english":"Did not","translit":"alam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَخْلُقكُّم","english":"We create you","translit":"nakhluqkkum","root":"خلق"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مِّن","english":"from","translit":"min","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَّآءٍۢ","english":"a water","translit":"māin","root":"موه"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مَّهِينٍۢ","english":"despicable","translit":"mahīnin","root":"مهن"}]},{"number":21,"translation":"And We placed it in a firm lodging","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَجَعَلْنَـٰهُ","english":"Then We placed it","translit":"fajaʿalnāhu","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِى","english":"in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَرَارٍۢ","english":"an abode","translit":"qarārin","root":"قرر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"مَّكِينٍ","english":"safe","translit":"makīnin","root":"مكن"}]},{"number":22,"translation":"For a known extent.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"For","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"قَدَرٍۢ","english":"a period","translit":"qadarin","root":"قدر"},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَّعْلُومٍۢ","english":"known","translit":"maʿlūmin","root":"علم"}]},{"number":23,"translation":"And We determined [it], and excellent [are We] to determine.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَقَدَرْنَا","english":"So We measured","translit":"faqadarnā","root":"قدر"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فَنِعْمَ","english":"and Best","translit":"faniʿ'ma","root":"نعم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْقَـٰدِرُونَ","english":"(are We to) measure","translit":"l-qādirūna","root":"قدر"}]},{"number":24,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":25,"translation":"Have We not made the earth a container","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَلَمْ","english":"Have not","translit":"alam","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"نَجْعَلِ","english":"We made","translit":"najʿali","root":"جعل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","english":"the earth","translit":"l-arḍa","root":"أرض"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كِفَاتًا","english":"a receptacle","translit":"kifātan","root":"كفت"}]},{"number":26,"translation":"Of the living and the dead?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"أَحْيَآءًۭ","english":"(For the) living","translit":"aḥyāan","root":"حيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَأَمْوَٰتًۭا","english":"and (the) dead","translit":"wa-amwātan","root":"موت"}]},{"number":27,"translation":"And We placed therein lofty, firmly set mountains and have given you to drink sweet water.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا","english":"And We made","translit":"wajaʿalnā","root":"جعل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"فِيهَا","english":"therein","translit":"fīhā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"رَوَٰسِىَ","english":"firmly set mountains","translit":"rawāsiya","root":"رسو"},{"position":4,"arabic":"شَـٰمِخَـٰتٍۢ","english":"lofty","translit":"shāmikhātin","root":"شمخ"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَأَسْقَيْنَـٰكُم","english":"and We gave you to drink","translit":"wa-asqaynākum","root":"سقي"},{"position":6,"arabic":"مَّآءًۭ","english":"water","translit":"māan","root":"موه"},{"position":7,"arabic":"فُرَاتًۭا","english":"sweet","translit":"furātan","root":"فرت"}]},{"number":28,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":29,"translation":"[They will be told], \"Proceed to that which you used to deny.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓا۟","english":"Proceed","translit":"inṭaliqū","root":"طلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"مَا","english":"what","translit":"mā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"كُنتُم","english":"you used to","translit":"kuntum","root":"كون"},{"position":5,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","english":"in it","translit":"bihi","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"تُكَذِّبُونَ","english":"deny","translit":"tukadhibūna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":30,"translation":"Proceed to a shadow [of smoke] having three columns","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓا۟","english":"Proceed","translit":"inṭaliqū","root":"طلق"},{"position":2,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ","english":"to","translit":"ilā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"ظِلٍّۢ","english":"a shadow","translit":"ẓillin","root":"ظلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ذِى","english":"having","translit":"dhī","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"ثَلَـٰثِ","english":"three","translit":"thalāthi","root":"ثلث"},{"position":6,"arabic":"شُعَبٍۢ","english":"columns","translit":"shuʿabin","root":"شعب"}]},{"number":31,"translation":"[But having] no cool shade and availing not against the flame.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"لَّا","english":"No","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ظَلِيلٍۢ","english":"cool shade","translit":"ẓalīlin","root":"ظلل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"and not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُغْنِى","english":"availing","translit":"yugh'nī","root":"غني"},{"position":5,"arabic":"مِنَ","english":"against","translit":"mina","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَبِ","english":"the flame","translit":"l-lahabi","root":"لهب"}]},{"number":32,"translation":"Indeed, it throws sparks [as huge] as a fortress,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّهَا","english":"Indeed, it","translit":"innahā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"تَرْمِى","english":"throws up","translit":"tarmī","root":"رمي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بِشَرَرٍۢ","english":"sparks","translit":"bishararin","root":"شرر"},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَٱلْقَصْرِ","english":"as the fortress","translit":"kal-qaṣri","root":"قصر"}]},{"number":33,"translation":"As if they were yellowish [black] camels.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ","english":"As if they (were)","translit":"ka-annahu","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"جِمَـٰلَتٌۭ","english":"camels","translit":"jimālatun","root":"جمل"},{"position":3,"arabic":"صُفْرٌۭ","english":"yellow","translit":"ṣuf'run","root":"صفر"}]},{"number":34,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":35,"translation":"This is a Day they will not speak,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is) a Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"يَنطِقُونَ","english":"they will speak","translit":"yanṭiqūna","root":"نطق"}]},{"number":36,"translation":"Nor will it be permitted for them to make an excuse.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَلَا","english":"And not","translit":"walā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يُؤْذَنُ","english":"will it be permitted","translit":"yu'dhanu","root":"أذن"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","english":"for them","translit":"lahum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"فَيَعْتَذِرُونَ","english":"to make excuses","translit":"fayaʿtadhirūna","root":"عذر"}]},{"number":37,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":38,"translation":"This is the Day of Judgement; We will have assembled you and the former peoples.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا","english":"This","translit":"hādhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمُ","english":"(is the) Day","translit":"yawmu","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلْفَصْلِ ۖ","english":"(of) Judgment","translit":"l-faṣli","root":"فصل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"جَمَعْنَـٰكُمْ","english":"We have gathered you","translit":"jamaʿnākum","root":"جمع","audio":"wbw/077_038_005.mp3"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","english":"and the former (people)","translit":"wal-awalīna","root":"أول","audio":"wbw/077_038_006.mp3"}]},{"number":39,"translation":"So if you have a plan, then plan against Me.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَإِن","english":"So if","translit":"fa-in","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","english":"is","translit":"kāna","root":"كون"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَكُمْ","english":"for you","translit":"lakum","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"كَيْدٌۭ","english":"a plan","translit":"kaydun","root":"كيد"},{"position":5,"arabic":"فَكِيدُونِ","english":"then plan against Me","translit":"fakīdūni","root":"كيد"}]},{"number":40,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":41,"translation":"Indeed, the righteous will be among shades and springs","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّ","english":"Indeed","translit":"inna","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ","english":"the righteous","translit":"l-mutaqīna","root":"وقي"},{"position":3,"arabic":"فِى","english":"(will be) in","translit":"fī","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ظِلَـٰلٍۢ","english":"shades","translit":"ẓilālin","root":"ظلل"},{"position":5,"arabic":"وَعُيُونٍۢ","english":"and springs","translit":"waʿuyūnin","root":"عين"}]},{"number":42,"translation":"And fruits from whatever they desire,","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ","english":"And fruits","translit":"wafawākiha","root":"فكه"},{"position":2,"arabic":"مِمَّا","english":"from what","translit":"mimmā","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"يَشْتَهُونَ","english":"they desire","translit":"yashtahūna","root":"شهو"}]},{"number":43,"translation":"[Being told], \"Eat and drink in satisfaction for what you used to do.\"","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كُلُوا۟","english":"Eat","translit":"kulū","root":"أكل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَٱشْرَبُوا۟","english":"and drink","translit":"wa-ish'rabū","root":"شرب"},{"position":3,"arabic":"هَنِيٓـًٔۢا","english":"(in) satisfaction","translit":"hanīan","root":"هنأ"},{"position":4,"arabic":"بِمَا","english":"for what","translit":"bimā","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","english":"you used to","translit":"kuntum","root":"كون"},{"position":6,"arabic":"تَعْمَلُونَ","english":"do","translit":"taʿmalūna","root":"عمل"}]},{"number":44,"translation":"Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"إِنَّا","english":"Indeed, We","translit":"innā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","english":"thus","translit":"kadhālika","root":""},{"position":3,"arabic":"نَجْزِى","english":"reward","translit":"najzī","root":"جزي"},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","english":"the good-doers","translit":"l-muḥ'sinīna","root":"حسن"}]},{"number":45,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":46,"translation":"[O disbelievers], eat and enjoy yourselves a little; indeed, you are criminals.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"كُلُوا۟","english":"Eat","translit":"kulū","root":"أكل"},{"position":2,"arabic":"وَتَمَتَّعُوا۟","english":"and enjoy yourselves","translit":"watamattaʿū","root":"متع"},{"position":3,"arabic":"قَلِيلًا","english":"a little","translit":"qalīlan","root":"قلل"},{"position":4,"arabic":"إِنَّكُم","english":"indeed, you","translit":"innakum","root":""},{"position":5,"arabic":"مُّجْرِمُونَ","english":"(are) criminals","translit":"muj'rimūna","root":"جرم"}]},{"number":47,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":48,"translation":"And when it is said to them, \"Bow [in prayer],\" they do not bow.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","english":"And when","translit":"wa-idhā","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"قِيلَ","english":"it is said","translit":"qīla","root":"قول"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لَهُمُ","english":"to them","translit":"lahumu","root":""},{"position":4,"arabic":"ٱرْكَعُوا۟","english":"Bow","translit":"ir'kaʿū","root":"ركع"},{"position":5,"arabic":"لَا","english":"not","translit":"lā","root":""},{"position":6,"arabic":"يَرْكَعُونَ","english":"they bow","translit":"yarkaʿūna","root":"ركع"}]},{"number":49,"translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"وَيْلٌۭ","english":"Woe","translit":"waylun","root":""},{"position":2,"arabic":"يَوْمَئِذٍۢ","english":"that Day","translit":"yawma-idhin","root":"يوم"},{"position":3,"arabic":"لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","english":"to the deniers","translit":"lil'mukadhibīna","root":"كذب"}]},{"number":50,"translation":"Then in what statement after the Qur'an will they believe?","words":[{"position":1,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ","english":"Then in what","translit":"fabi-ayyi","root":"أيي"},{"position":2,"arabic":"حَدِيثٍۭ","english":"statement","translit":"ḥadīthin","root":"حدث"},{"position":3,"arabic":"بَعْدَهُۥ","english":"after it","translit":"baʿdahu","root":"بعد"},{"position":4,"arabic":"يُؤْمِنُونَ","english":"will they believe","translit":"yu'minūna","root":"أمن"}]}]}
